---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import LessonNav from '../../components/LessonNav.astro';
import LessonAudio from '../../components/LessonAudio.astro';
---
<Layout title="Lesson 10: Spotlight Pages">
  <div class="lesson-header">
    <span class="lesson-badge">Lesson 10</span>
    <h1>Spotlight Pages</h1>
    <p class="lesson-subtitle">Dedicate a page to something cool about your team and make it stand out.</p>
    <LessonAudio slug="lesson-9" />
  </div>

  <p>
    Spotlight pages are where you go deep on one specific thing your team did that you're proud of.
    It could be a mechanism, an outreach event, a cool initiative, a design challenge you solved, 
    or really anything that makes your team unique. These pages give judges a closer look at what 
    sets you apart.
  </p>

  <!-- What is a Spotlight Page -->
  <div class="intro-card">
    <div class="intro-icon">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 style="margin-top:0;">What's a Spotlight Page?</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0;">
        A <strong>single page</strong> dedicated to one topic that deserves extra attention. Instead of cramming 
        it into another section, you give it room to breathe with photos, details, and context that 
        really show off the work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- What You Can Spotlight -->
  <h2>What You Can Spotlight</h2>
  <p>Pretty much anything your team is proud of. Here are some ideas:</p>
  <div class="ideas-grid">
    <div class="idea-card">
      <span class="idea-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 1v4M12 19v4M4.22 4.22l2.83 2.83M16.95 16.95l2.83 2.83M1 12h4M19 12h4M4.22 19.78l2.83-2.83M16.95 7.05l2.83-2.83"/></svg>
      </span>
      <strong>A Mechanism</strong>
      <span class="idea-desc">Your intake, launcher, climb system, or any standout subsystem</span>
    </div>
    <div class="idea-card">
      <span class="idea-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
      </span>
      <strong>An Outreach Event</strong>
      <span class="idea-desc">A workshop you ran, a demo day, mentoring younger teams</span>
    </div>
    <div class="idea-card">
      <span class="idea-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
      </span>
      <strong>A Team Initiative</strong>
      <span class="idea-desc">Mentorship program, team training system, new member onboarding</span>
    </div>
    <div class="idea-card">
      <span class="idea-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
      </span>
      <strong>A Design Challenge</strong>
      <span class="idea-desc">A hard problem you solved, multiple iterations, before/after</span>
    </div>
    <div class="idea-card">
      <span class="idea-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
      </span>
      <strong>Software Feature</strong>
      <span class="idea-desc">Computer vision pipeline, custom path planning, dashboard tool</span>
    </div>
    <div class="idea-card">
      <span class="idea-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
      </span>
      <strong>Something Unique</strong>
      <span class="idea-desc">Custom field element, 3D printing setup, team branding system</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Layout Tips -->
  <h2>How to Lay Out a Spotlight Page</h2>
  <p>There's no single right way to do it, but here are a few proven formats:</p>

  <div class="layout-tips">
    <div class="layout-tip">
      <span class="tip-num">1</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Hero Photo + Story</strong>
        <span class="tip-desc">Lead with one big, high-quality photo at the top. Below it, write a short paragraph about what it is, why it matters, and what went into it. Keep the text tight.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="layout-tip">
      <span class="tip-num">2</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Before & After</strong>
        <span class="tip-desc">Show two images side by side (or top/bottom) with captions. Great for design iterations, outreach growth, or mechanism revisions.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="layout-tip">
      <span class="tip-num">3</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Photo Grid + Callouts</strong>
        <span class="tip-desc">Use 3-4 photos in a grid and add small labels or annotations. Works well for events where you want to show the scope of what happened.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="layout-tip">
      <span class="tip-num">4</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Timeline Strip</strong>
        <span class="tip-desc">Show how something evolved over time with a few milestones. Good for mechanisms that went through multiple versions or events you ran more than once.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="layout-tip">
      <span class="tip-num">5</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Stats + Visuals</strong>
        <span class="tip-desc">Lead with a few key numbers (hours spent, people reached, iterations tested) and back them up with photos and a brief explanation.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Sample Layouts -->
  <h2>Example Layouts</h2>
  <p>Here are three common spotlight page formats you can adapt:</p>

  <div class="samples-row">
    <!-- Layout A: Hero Photo + Story -->
    <div class="sample-wrap">
      <div class="sample-page">
        <div class="sp-header">Mechanism Spotlight</div>
        <div class="sp-body">
          <div class="sp-hero-img"></div>
          <div class="sp-title-line"></div>
          <div class="sp-text-block">
            <div class="sp-line"></div>
            <div class="sp-line" style="width:90%;"></div>
            <div class="sp-line" style="width:75%;"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-stats-row">
            <div class="sp-stat">
              <span class="sp-stat-num">3</span>
              <span class="sp-stat-label">Iterations</span>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-stat">
              <span class="sp-stat-num">2.1s</span>
              <span class="sp-stat-label">Cycle Time</span>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-stat">
              <span class="sp-stat-num">40+</span>
              <span class="sp-stat-label">Hours</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-text-block">
            <div class="sp-line" style="width:85%;"></div>
            <div class="sp-line" style="width:60%;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="sample-label">Hero Photo + Story</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Layout B: Before & After -->
    <div class="sample-wrap">
      <div class="sample-page">
        <div class="sp-header">Design Evolution</div>
        <div class="sp-body">
          <div class="sp-title-line"></div>
          <div class="sp-compare-row">
            <div class="sp-compare-col">
              <div class="sp-compare-img before"></div>
              <span class="sp-compare-label">V1 - Prototype</span>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-compare-arrow">&#8594;</div>
            <div class="sp-compare-col">
              <div class="sp-compare-img after"></div>
              <span class="sp-compare-label">V3 - Final</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-callout">
            <div class="sp-callout-dot"></div>
            <div class="sp-text-block" style="flex:1;">
              <div class="sp-line"></div>
              <div class="sp-line" style="width:80%;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-callout">
            <div class="sp-callout-dot"></div>
            <div class="sp-text-block" style="flex:1;">
              <div class="sp-line" style="width:90%;"></div>
              <div class="sp-line" style="width:65%;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-text-block">
            <div class="sp-line" style="width:75%;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="sample-label">Before & After</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Layout C: Photo Grid + Callouts -->
    <div class="sample-wrap">
      <div class="sample-page">
        <div class="sp-header">Outreach Event</div>
        <div class="sp-body">
          <div class="sp-title-line"></div>
          <div class="sp-photo-grid">
            <div class="sp-grid-img"></div>
            <div class="sp-grid-img"></div>
            <div class="sp-grid-img"></div>
            <div class="sp-grid-img"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-stats-row">
            <div class="sp-stat">
              <span class="sp-stat-num">120</span>
              <span class="sp-stat-label">Attendees</span>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-stat">
              <span class="sp-stat-num">5</span>
              <span class="sp-stat-label">Stations</span>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-stat">
              <span class="sp-stat-num">8hr</span>
              <span class="sp-stat-label">Duration</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-text-block">
            <div class="sp-line"></div>
            <div class="sp-line" style="width:85%;"></div>
            <div class="sp-line" style="width:70%;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="sample-label">Photo Grid + Stats</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Writing Tips -->
  <h2>Writing Tips</h2>
  <div class="writing-grid">
    <div class="writing-card">
      <span class="writing-num">1</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Be Specific</strong>
        <span class="writing-desc">Don't say "we improved our intake." Say "we reduced jam rate from 40% to under 5% by adding a compliant roller."</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="writing-card">
      <span class="writing-num">2</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Include Numbers</strong>
        <span class="writing-desc">Hours spent, people involved, versions tested, speed improvements. Numbers make your work feel real.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="writing-card">
      <span class="writing-num">3</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Show the Problem First</strong>
        <span class="writing-desc">Explain what wasn't working before you explain how you fixed it. This gives judges context and makes your solution more impressive.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="writing-card">
      <span class="writing-num">4</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Let Photos Do Work</strong>
        <span class="writing-desc">One great photo with a caption often says more than a paragraph. Don't over-explain things you can show visually.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Typical Length -->
  <div class="length-card">
    <div class="length-header">
      <span class="length-label">Typical Length</span>
      <span class="length-badge">1 page each</span>
    </div>
    <p style="margin:.5rem 0 0;">
      Keep each spotlight to <strong>one page</strong>. The goal is to go deeper on one thing, not to 
      write an essay. If you have room in your portfolio, you can include multiple spotlight pages 
      on different topics.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Remember -->
  <div class="remember-card">
    <div class="remember-icon">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong style="font-size:1.05rem;">Pick What You're Proudest Of</strong>
      <p style="margin:.35rem 0 0;">
        Don't force a spotlight page for the sake of having one. Pick something your team genuinely 
        cares about and let that energy come through. Judges can tell when a team is excited about 
        their work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <LessonNav 
    prev={{ title: "Business & Community Impact", href: "/lessons/lesson-8/" }}
  />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Intro hero card */
  .intro-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
  }
  .intro-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  .intro-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* Ideas grid */
  .ideas-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .idea-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .5rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s, transform .2s;
  }
  .idea-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .idea-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    color: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .idea-desc {
    font-size: .92rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Layout tips */
  .layout-tips {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .75rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .layout-tip {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 1.15rem 1.25rem;
    transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
  }
  .layout-tip:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  .tip-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: .95rem;
  }
  .layout-tip div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .25rem;
  }
  .tip-desc {
    font-size: .9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  /* Sample layout pages */
  .samples-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .sample-wrap {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .5rem;
  }
  .sample-label {
    font-size: .82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .sample-page {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 8.5 / 11;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  /* Shared sample-page internals */
  .sp-header {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.6rem;
    text-align: center;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .04em;
  }
  .sp-body {
    padding: 0.6rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.45rem;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .sp-hero-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 0;
    padding-bottom: 45%;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    border: 1.5px dashed var(--border-accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }
  .sp-title-line {
    height: 7px;
    width: 55%;
    background: var(--text-heading);
    border-radius: 3px;
    opacity: .25;
  }
  .sp-text-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.18rem;
  }
  .sp-line {
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--bg-surface-hover);
    border-radius: 3px;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .sp-stats-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .sp-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.05rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    flex: 1;
  }
  .sp-stat-num {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .sp-stat-label {
    font-size: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .03em;
  }

  /* Before & After compare */
  .sp-compare-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }
  .sp-compare-col {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }
  .sp-compare-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 0;
    padding-bottom: 70%;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border: 1.5px dashed var(--border);
  }
  .sp-compare-img.before {
    background: var(--bg-surface-hover);
    border-color: var(--border);
  }
  .sp-compare-img.after {
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    border-color: var(--border-accent);
  }
  .sp-compare-label {
    font-size: 0.42rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .sp-compare-arrow {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .sp-callout {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }
  .sp-callout-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  /* Photo grid */
  .sp-photo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  .sp-grid-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 0;
    padding-bottom: 70%;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    border: 1.5px dashed var(--border-accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  /* Writing tips */
  .writing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .writing-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 1.15rem 1.25rem;
    transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s, transform .2s;
  }
  .writing-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .writing-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: .95rem;
  }
  .writing-card div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .25rem;
  }
  .writing-desc {
    font-size: .9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  /* Length card */
  .length-card {
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
  }
  .length-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  .length-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .length-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  .length-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    padding: .25rem .85rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: .92rem;
  }

  /* Remember highlight */
  .remember-card {
    display: flex;
